mapper.select: SELECT A."hiHokenshaNo" AS "被保険者番号", A."shotokuHantei_shikibetsuCode" AS "識別コード", A."serviceTeikyoYM" AS "サービス提供年月", A."shokisaiHokenshaNo" AS "証記載保険者番号", A."hokenRiyoshaFutangaku" AS "利用者負担額", A."sikyugaku" AS "支給予定額", A."setaiCode" AS "世帯コード", A."shotokuHantei_shichosonCode" AS "市町村コード", A."beikoKojinshotokuKubun" AS "備考欄個人所得区分", PSM."meisho" AS "被保険者名", C."yokaigoJotaiKubunCode" AS "要介護認定状態区分コード", C."kyuSochishaFlag" AS "旧措置者フラグ", C."ninteiYukoKikanKaishiYMD" AS "認定有効期間開始年月日", C."ninteiYukoKikanShuryoYMD" AS "認定有効期間終了年月日", PSM."kanaMeisho" AS "カナ名称", PSM."yubinNo" AS "郵便番号", PSM."choikiCode" AS "町域コード", PSM."jusho"||PSM."banchi"||PSM."katagaki" AS "住所番地方書", PSM."gyoseikuCode" AS "行政区コード", PSM."gyoseikuName" AS "行政区", D."shichosonCode"||D."koikinaiTokureiSochimotoShichosonCode" AS "措置元市町村コード", D."idoJiyuCode" AS "異動事由コード", D."shikakuShutokuJiyuCode" as "資格取得事由コード", D."shikakuSoshitsuJiyuCode" AS "資格喪失事由コード", D."shikakuHenkoJiyuCode" AS "資格変更事由コード", D."jushochitokureiTekiyoJiyuCode" as "住所地特例適用事由コード", D."jushochitokureiKaijoJiyuCode" AS "住所地特例解除事由コード" FROM rgdb."TempKyufujissekiTyukann9" AS A INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT4001JukyushaDaicho" AS C ON C."hihokenshaNo" = A."hiHokenshaNo" INNER JOIN rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" AS D ON D."hihokenshaNo" = A."hiHokenshaNo" LEFT OUTER JOIN rgua.${宛名識別対象PSM} AS PSM ON PSM."shikibetsuCode" = A."shotokuHantei_shikibetsuCode" WHERE C."yukoMukoKubun" = '1' AND C."chokkinFlag" =TRUE
